{"tid":1490971,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Rockstar North 一些動作暗示離《GTA 6》的推出已經不遠了？","createTime":"2019-08-20T09:01:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T07:31:22.000Z","uid":85180,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d4e60fb5ed0a227b0252e48ccec48e0c1cf8f6d8","tid":1490971,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:01:43.000Z","msg":"Rockstar North 一些動作暗示離《GTA 6》的推出已經不遠了？<br />\n<img src=\"https://news.xfastest.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/GTAOnline_Casino-500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2FGTAOnline_Casino-500.jpg&h=99534759&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nR星旗下有著搖錢樹 IP 的《GTA》系列，似乎新作短期內就會有些頭緒了！<br />\n<br />\n近日據外媒報導指出，英國 Rockstar North 辦公室已經撤下了《碧血狂殺 2》的宣傳布條，外界紛紛認為這是《GTA 6》即將推出的線索之一。之所以有此猜測，是因為在《碧血狂殺 2》布條懸掛於此之前，被撤下的布條的就是《GTA 5》。<br />\n<br />\n關於《GTA 6》遊戲內容傳言可以說是眾說紛紜，其中近期的爆料指出，遊戲劇情類似當紅美劇《毒梟》，另外消息也指出，由於記憶體容量限制，新作《GTA6》將無法在 PS4 等舊款家機上運行，只能在 PS5、Xbox Scarlett 等新世代主機上運行。<br />\n<br />\n另外雖然明天就是科隆 Gamescom 遊戲展開幕的日子，但 R 星應該不會有任何新消息釋出，玩家們只能繼續期待網路上有些內線消息釋出。"},{"pid":"c74a5974b70482d729a3295557e81eead00632db","tid":1490971,"uid":81113,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:03:50.000Z","msg":"PS4 pro都唔得？又要交錢續期了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9FY0tQU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9FY0tQU.gif&h=2a7166e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17a543a8b0a0c80be2baa2e0f664fe0c08609ef1","tid":1490971,"uid":203918,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:05:56.000Z","msg":"有人話係bully2"},{"pid":"0b2ee832d4941c0ee6fe5258c78817b68f1ad6bf","tid":1490971,"uid":5499,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:09:00.000Z","msg":"香港日日都gta"},{"pid":"9ae104bd6baf52ab9e9cfd3c8503744e5956f275","tid":1490971,"uid":11719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cit